    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stencil technique of printing in which ink or dye is forced through a mesh, traditionally silk, on which a design has been formed by stopping out certain areas. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
